SS(x_0,y_0,r^*)
 SS(x_0,y_0,r)=\sum_{i=1}^{n}\left(\sqrt{(x_i-x_0)^2 + (y_i-y_0)^2}-r\right)^2. 
 0=\frac{\partial}{\partial r}SS(x_0,y_0,r)=-2\left(\sum_{i=1}^{n}\sqrt{(x_i-x_0)^2+(y_i-y_0)^2}-nr\right), 
 r^{*}=\frac{1}{n}\sum_{i=1}^{n}\sqrt{(x_i-x_0)^2+(y_i-y_0)^2}. 
